#* '''1742''', {{w|Edward Young}}, ''[[w:Night Thoughts (poem)|Night Thoughts on Life, Death and Immortality]]'' I, 1, [http://books.google.com/books?id=rtJbAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA95&dq=procrastination+intitle:night+intitle:thoughts&lr=lang_en&as_brr=0&ei=sve2SKSzKYXKzQSanZmnCA#PPA95,M1 393]
